Installing the code
----------------------
1. install apache2
	$sudo apt-get install apache2
	$sudo service apache2 start
2. start apache2 webserver
	$sudo service apache2 start
3. untar demopage.tar in your home area
4. using superuser create softlink of index.html and img directory in /var/www/html/
	# cd /var/www/html/
	# ln -s <your home>/demopage/index.html index.html
	# ln -s <your home>/demopage/img img
5. service apache2 restart

Naming conventions
------------------------

1. the input images are named as m1.jpg m2.jpg etc..
2. the output images should be kept under img/output/
3. naming convention m1-<Language>.jpg, m2-<Language>.jpg

Adding new images
--------------------

1. Edit code starting line 24 till 29 in index.html to add new images to the list, name as per the convention specified above.
2. Add the output images to img/output/ directory using nameing convention specified above.

Adding new languages
---------------------
1. Edit the code section between line 37 to 40 
